Short: Generate weather-tables, Towns, and NPC-Lists for RPGs (DSA)
Type: game/role
Author: Henning Peters <faroul@beyond.hb.north.de>
Uploader: Henning Peters <faroul@beyond.hb.north.de>

Three little programs to generate weather-tables, towns, and lists of
"enemies" for Fantasy-Role-Playing-Games (esp. the "enemy-list" is for the
german "Das Schwarze Auge"). You need a running LaTeX environment!
German texts, Public-Domain, source in Pascal included and may be altered
for other systems (then send source to the author, please).

Drei kleine Programme, mit denen man Wetter-Listen, Doerfer und Gegner-
Tabellen fuer Fantasy-Rollenspiele erstellen kann (insbesondere letzteres
fuer "Das Schwarze Auge"). Eine LaTeX-Installation ist notwendig!
Public-Domain, Quellcode in Pascal enthalten, darf zwecks Systemanpassung
verändert werden (dann bitte an Autor schicken).

	Faroul

